  "dialogue": [
    {
      "content": "早啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:36",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "在干嘛？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "不早了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "中午好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "我在忙工作啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "，知道你在忙工作，你说过了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "具体在干什么",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "在和编辑对序的内容要怎么写",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "你说的是书开头的序言吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "哈哈，那个我以为都是瞎写的，这也是认真商量过的结果吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "做书的每一步都是认认真真的，没有随便瞎搞的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "不排除做烂书来圈钱的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "虽然我也知道这种东西，根本没什么人会认真看",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "你是说序言还是你的书？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "我本来说的是序言",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是我的书可能也不是这个下场吧hhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "谢谢你的提醒啊！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "[[sticker:uploads/upload_1772004899068193972.jpg]]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhhhhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "我不是故意的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "哥哥不会怪我吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "你真是我的好妹妹啊！（咬牙切齿",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "你凶我。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "抱歉，一下子找不到滑跪的表情",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "[[sticker:uploads/upload_1771889295918185192.jpg]]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "给我记账上吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "，你什么时候有这份账的？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "我怎么不知道我给你记账",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "是不是把我和别的女的搞混了？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "我哪里有别的女的？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "我以为你会在心里给我默默记下来",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "小林今天说对了一句话加分，小林今天又说错了一句话，扣分",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "？？？少自恋了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "谁对你这么关心呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "啊 糟糕，我又要扣分了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为我太自恋了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh不是说了没有扣分这回事吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为我已经沉浸在演戏中，不知天地为何物",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "演什么戏？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "配合你的出演",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以你刚是在COS突然情绪来了，想给哥哥找茬的妹妹吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "咋理解的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "我只是想突然耍一下骄横，逗你一下",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "[[sticker:uploads/upload_1771889369318410004.png]]好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "那我的思路全歪了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh，难道要我叫你公主大人？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh你是这么油腻的人吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "怎么想出那么油腻的回答？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也觉得有些油腻打出来的时候，甚至感到了一丝羞耻",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "但我现在脑子有点不够用了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "被编辑催的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "只能想出这么不走心套公式的回复了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "算了，你们忙就不要回我了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "还好，我尽量长点脑子回来",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "脑子脑子快快回来",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "这种念咒真的有用吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "我希望有用",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "对了，你会不会自言自语啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "会啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "你说的自言自语是哪种？应该不是陆小葵要加油的那种吧？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "不过有时候压力很大或者心情很低落的时候，会照着镜子说点话",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "你都说什么，是打气的话吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "差不多吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "有时候也会说，算了算了，活过一天是一天",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以你刚才自言自语了吗？也是自言自语，跟自己打气？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "差不多吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "我自言自语跟自己聊了会天",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "是因为太无聊了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，之前没和你说，我一个跟我一起上晚班，中间的同事调走了嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "原来你还有同事跟你一起上班的，我一直以为你都是一个人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "我去过好多便利店，都是一个人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "我只有上晚班，在中间这个部分有两个人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "其他时候也是一个人上班",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "本来之前这段时间就不好熬，有一个人还能聊天，结果现在他揍走了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "他为什么要走了？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "我们这家店效益一般，他好像是要升职吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "他本来就是管培生，现在调到中心店去了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "除了少一个人说话，你会觉得有点失落吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "看到身边的人在往上走",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "是有一点",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "他也跟我是差不多时候进来的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "唉",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "同事的成功更令人痛心",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "你会不会觉得我很小心眼？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "这也算小心眼吗？那世上没有心眼大的人了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "这是人之常情啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "我看到跟我同期的同事在评级的事情上走的比我快",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也会有一点暗戳戳的失落",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你会觉得焦虑吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "焦虑好像还好，也没什么",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "我好像就是这么的不上进",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "本来就挺失落，又无聊了，不要再在自己身上找问题了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "这不钻进牛角尖了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "可我就是觉得我好不上进啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "你想啊，跟我同龄的人都在往上走，甚至我同班的同事都调到中心店了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "但我一点都不觉得焦虑，只觉得少一个人跟我聊天好无聊，",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "但凡我要是上心一点，我现在应该都不会觉得失落吧嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得你没有一次感到焦虑，最重要的原因是你本来就没有想在这个行业长期发展啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "你一开始就不是管培生",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "你之前也和我说了要转行，这行又不是你的长久之计",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以看到同事走了，你当然不会觉得焦虑了，他走的路，不是你想走的路",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "豁然开朗！！！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "老师！！！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "我无端成了人生导师吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh你不是吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "你经常给我一些人生的金玉良言",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "我好像没有和你说过，你也是我的人生导师",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "没有啊，你从来没跟我说过啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "而且我到底哪里是你的人生导师了，我有说过什么有意义的话吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "那就是我放在心里了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "没想到要告诉你",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "好你无意间透露的生活态度，有给我启发",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "就比如说你的职业",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "你什么意思？你不是在阴阳怪气我吧？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "12:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "品出了阴阳怪气的意思",
